  <brief_title>A Trial of Ciclesonide in Adults With Mild-to-moderate COVID-19</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Trial of Ciclesonide to Assess The Antiviral Effect for Adults With Mild-to-moderate COVID-19</official_title>
